7506 B9          7 936 cp      c                           ; is the new potential = board potential?
7507 28 05       7 937 jr      z, Potentials_Increment     ; yes, increment attack mobility
7509 30 04       7 938 jr      nc, Potentials_Update       ; if (new potential > board potential) update and skip
750B 4F          7 939 ld      c, a                        ; board potential = new potential
750C 06 00       7 940 ld      b, 0                        ; restart attack mobility
750E             7 941 Potentials_Increment
750E 04          7 942 inc     b                           ; increment attack mobility
750F             7 943 Potentials_Update
750F 77          7 944 ld      (hl), a                     ; save potential in the cell pointed by HL
