76D5             9 9 ; Sound_FX: play a sound effect (tone) defined by many parameters
76D5             9 10 ; 
76D5             9 11 ; Input:    IX = tone parameters address
76D5             9 12 ;
76D5             9 13 ; Output:   -
76D5             9 14 ;
76D5             9 15 ; Destroys: A, BC, DE, HL, IY
